Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.07,OP4R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Se-no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:03.08,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Demo sonnan ja dame
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:05.11,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Mou sonna ja hora
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:09.39,OP4R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Kokoro wa shinka suru yo motto motto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.98,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Kotoba ni sureba kiechau kankei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:29.26,OP4R,,0,0,0,,nara kotoba wo keseba ii ya tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.87,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Omotteta osoreteta dakedo are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.08,OP4R,,0,0,0,,nanka chigau ka mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.14,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Senri no michi mo ippo kara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.32,OP4R,,0,0,0,,ishi no you ni katai sonna ishi de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.32,OP4R,,0,0,0,,chiri mo tsumoreba yamato nadeshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.38,OP4R,,0,0,0,,shii nuki de iya shinu ki de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:45.76,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Fuwafuwari fuwafuwaru anata ga namae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.33,OP4R,,0,0,0,,wo yobu sore dake de chuu e ukabu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:53.88,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Fuwafuwaru fuwafuwari anata ga watte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:57.30,OP4R,,0,0,0,,iru sore dake de egao ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:05.33,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Kami-sama arigatou unmei no itazura demo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:13.08,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Meguriaeta koto ga shiawase na no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.09,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Demo sonnan ja dame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:17.09,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Mou sonna ja hora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:21.02,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Kokoro wa shinka suru yo motto motto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:23.10,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Sou sonnan ja iya da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.10,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Nee sonna ja mada
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.62,OP4R,,0,0,0,,Watashi no koto mitete ne zutto zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.96,OP4E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:03.08,OP4E,,0,0,0,,But that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:05.11,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Look, with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:09.39,OP4E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}my heart is evolving more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.98,OP4E,,0,0,0,,If the relationship will disappear when we put
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:29.26,OP4E,,0,0,0,,we put it into words, we should just do away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.87,OP4E,,0,0,0,,I thought this, and I was afraid, but what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.08,OP4E,,0,0,0,,I think something is different, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.14,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Even the longest path starts with one step
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:37.32,OP4E,,0,0,0,,so I'll make my resolve as hard as stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.32,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Many little things add to Yamato Nadeshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.38,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Selflessly, no, recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:49.33,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Softly, gently, with just you calling my name, I float up into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:57.30,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Gently, softly, with just your laugh, a smile comes to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:05.33,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God, even if it's a prank of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:13.08,OP4E,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I could meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.09,OP4E,,0,0,0,,But that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:17.09,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Look, with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:21.02,OP4E,,0,0,0,,my heart is evolving more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:23.10,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Right, we can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.10,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Hey, that'll come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.62,OP4E,,0,0,0,,Look at me, okay? Always, always.
